trans-unit.source: Reads return values from HTTP response text for Web service clients implemented using HTTP but without SOAP.
trans-unit.target: Leseoperasjoner returnere verdier fra HTTP-svartekst for Web service-klienter implementert ved hjelp av HTTP, men uten SOAP.

trans-unit.source: TextReturnReader and other classes in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols> namespace support the .NET Framework's implementations of Web services via the HTTP-GET and HTTP-POST operations.
trans-unit.target: TextReturnReader og andre klasser i den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols>navneområdet støtter .NET Framework-implementeringer av webtjenester via HTTP-GET og HTTP-POST-operasjoner.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols>

trans-unit.source: Web service writers and readers serialize and deserialize, respectively, between the parameters or return objects of Web methods and the HTTP request or response streams.
trans-unit.target: Web service forfattere lesere serialisere og deserialisere henholdsvis mellom parameterne eller return objekter av Web-metoder og HTTP-forespørselen eller svar dataflytene.

trans-unit.source: Web service writers and readers use HTTP for transport but don't exchange messages using the SOAP standard.
trans-unit.target: Web service forfattere og lesere bruke HTTP til transport, men exchange ikke meldinger ved hjelp av SOAP-standard.

trans-unit.source: The TextReturnReader class implements the client-side reading of non-XML text into Web method return values.
trans-unit.target: TextReturnReader klassen implementerer klientsiden lesing av ikke-XML-teksten i returverdier for Web-metoden.

trans-unit.source: To obtain a return value, the text, which is encoded in the body of an HTTP response, is parsed using regular expression pattern matching, as specified by the attribute <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MatchAttribute>, which can be applied to a Web method in a client proxy class.
trans-unit.target: For å få en returverdi er tekst, som kodes i brødteksten i en HTTP-svar, analyseres med samsvarende av RegEx-mønster som angitt av attributtet <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MatchAttribute>, som kan brukes i en Web-metoden i en klient proxy klasse.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MatchAttribute>

trans-unit.source: The TextReturnReader class calls the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher> class to actually perform the pattern matching.
trans-unit.target: TextReturnReader klassen kall av <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher>klassen for å utføre faktisk mønsteret samsvarende.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher>

trans-unit.source: Text pattern matching provides a way for Web services to retrieve HTML content without converting it to XML documents that must be bound to XML Schema definitions.
trans-unit.target: Teksten mønsteret samsvarende gjør det mulig for webtjenester til å hente HTML-innhold uten å konvertere XML-dokumentene som må være bundet til definisjoner av XML-skjema.

trans-unit.source: Regular expression search targets are specified in a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document via `match` XML elements within `text` elements.
trans-unit.target: RegEx Søk mål er angitt i et dokument Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL) via `match` XML-elementer i `text` elementer.

trans-unit.source: Both elements belong to the namespace http://microsoft.com/wsdl/mime/textMatching/.
trans-unit.target: Begge elementer tilhøre navneområdet http://microsoft.com/wsdl/mime/textMatching/.

trans-unit.source: When **match** elements are specified in a WSDL document, the Wsdl.exe tool applies <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MatchAttribute> attributes to the corresponding Web methods in the client proxy class that is generated.
trans-unit.target: Når **samsvarer med** elementer som er angitt i et WSDL-dokument, verktøyet Wsdl.exe gjelder <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MatchAttribute>attributter til de tilsvarende Web metodene i klienten proxy-klassen som er generert.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MatchAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Also, TextReturnReader is used in place of <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.XmlReturnReader>, the default class for deserializing Web method return values according to the .NET Framework's implementations of Web services via the HTTP-GET and HTTP-POST operations.
trans-unit.target: Også TextReturnReader brukes i stedet for <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.XmlReturnReader>, standard-klasse for deserialisering av Web-metoden returnere verdier i henhold til .NET Framework-implementeringer av webtjenester via HTTP-GET og HTTP-POST-operasjoner.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.XmlReturnReader>

trans-unit.source: You typically will not need to use the TextReturnReader class directly.
trans-unit.target: Du trenger vanligvis ikke å bruke klassen TextReturnReader direkte.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns an initializer for the specified method.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en initialisering for den angitte metoden.

trans-unit.source: An initializer is an object passed as a parameter to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Initialize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: En initialisering er et objekt som ble sendt som en parameter i <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Initialize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader> class, the initializer is a <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher> object based on the return type of the Web method.
trans-unit.target: For den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader>klassen initialiseringen er en <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher>objekt basert på Returtypen for Web-metoden.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader>

trans-unit.source: The GetInitializer method is invoked during service initialization.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetInitializer aktiveres under initialisering av tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: Later, at the time a response is processed, the initializer object is passed to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Initialize%2A> method of another <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader> instance.
trans-unit.target: Senere, da svar behandles, initialisering-objektet er sendt til den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Initialize%2A>-metoden til et annet <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader>forekomsten.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: The other instance performs the actual reading.
trans-unit.target: Den andre forekomsten utfører den faktiske lesing.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"></xref> that specifies the Web method for which the initializer is obtained.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"> </xref> som angir Web-metoden i initialisering hentes.

trans-unit.source: An initializer for the specified method
trans-unit.target: En initialisering for den angitte metoden

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en forekomst.

trans-unit.source: The Initialize method supplies the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher> object used by the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Read%2A> method to parse text contained in the HTTP response.
trans-unit.target: I initialiseringsmetoden leverer den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher>objekt som brukes av den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Read%2A>metode for å analysere teksten i HTTP-svar.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Read%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher>

trans-unit.source: The Initialize method is invoked at the time a request is processed.
trans-unit.target: I initialiseringsmetoden aktiveres når en forespørselen behandles.

trans-unit.source: The input parameter, `o`, is obtained by calling the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.GetInitializer%2A> method on another instance of the class that is obtained during client initialization.
trans-unit.target: Inndataparameteren `o`, hentes ved å ringe det <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.GetInitializer%2A>-metode på en annen forekomst av klassen som er hentet under initialisering av klienten.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.GetInitializer%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher"></xref> object for the return type of the Web method being invoked.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher"> </xref> objekt for Returtypen for Web-metoden blir aktivert.

trans-unit.source: Parses text contained in the HTTP response.
trans-unit.target: Analyserer teksten i HTTP-svar.

trans-unit.source: To parse the text content of the HTTP response, the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader> class's implementation of the Read method uses the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher> object passed as an argument to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Initialize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Analysere tekstinnhold av HTTP-svar i <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader>klassens implementering av metoden lese bruker den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher>objekt sendt som et argument til den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Initialize%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader.Initialize%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.PatternMatcher> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.TextReturnReader>

trans-unit.source: It closes the response stream before returning the deserialized Web method return value.
trans-unit.target: Den lukker dataflyten svar før den returnerer deserialisert Web metoden returverdien.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Net.WebResponse> object containing the output message for an operation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Net.WebResponse>objektet som inneholder utdatameldingen for en operasjon.</xref:System.Net.WebResponse>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.IO.Stream> whose content is the body of the HTTP response represented by the `response` parameter.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.IO.Stream>filreferanser meldingsteksten i HTTP-svar representeres av den `response` parameteren.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: An object containing the deserialized Web method return value.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som inneholder metoden deserialisert Web returverdi.
